WEBVTT

00:13.240 --> 00:16.450
They fought south of the city,
and died north of the wall.

00:14.300 --> 00:16.770
[Yongzhou]

00:16.480 --> 00:19.710
Left out in the wild, unburied,
for the crows to peck and gnaw.

00:19.710 --> 00:23.160
Tell the crows for me: eat well,
feast your fill.

00:23.280 --> 00:28.120
Left in the wild, surely unburied—
how could rotten flesh escape your beak?

00:28.120 --> 00:29.670
Well, Xiao Wuyi...

00:30.350 --> 00:31.950
After all these years of war,

00:32.580 --> 00:35.040
you still haven't earned
a good reputation.

00:35.380 --> 00:38.360
[Yang Yi's Mansion, Armory Director]

00:41.110 --> 00:43.620
[Li Mao, Prince of Qi, styled Yizhi]

00:48.110 --> 00:48.880
This family

00:49.320 --> 00:51.450
seems to have been gone for a long time.

00:52.000 --> 00:52.560
Da.

00:53.430 --> 00:54.430
Everyone is gone.

00:54.710 --> 00:55.970
How am I supposed to look into this?

00:55.970 --> 00:59.030
[Da, guard to the Prince of Qi]

01:00.430 --> 01:02.290
I need to tell Wuyi about all this.

02:41.860 --> 02:45.230
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

02:45.610 --> 02:48.130
[Episode 3]

02:54.800 --> 02:55.560
Yizhi!

03:00.960 --> 03:01.470
Wuyi.

03:03.240 --> 03:03.840
Wuyi.

03:05.150 --> 03:06.480
What are you doing here?

03:06.560 --> 03:07.760
I was waiting for you.

03:09.470 --> 03:10.800
Xiao Wuyi!

03:12.430 --> 03:13.960
How did you know
I was coming back to the capital today?

03:13.960 --> 03:15.400
In your letter, you said
you were coming back by water.

03:15.400 --> 03:16.800
Counting the days, it had to be today,

03:16.800 --> 03:17.960
so I came here to wait for you.

03:17.960 --> 03:20.190
I heard the battle at Jiuzhang Plain
was especially brutal.

03:20.190 --> 03:20.850
How are you?

03:20.910 --> 03:22.240
Let me have a look at you.

03:23.710 --> 03:24.240
I'm fine.

03:25.190 --> 03:26.190
You've been traveling day and night
this whole way.

03:26.190 --> 03:27.390
You must be starving.

03:27.400 --> 03:29.000
I brought your favorite taro pastries.

03:29.000 --> 03:30.060
Hurry and try some.

03:31.560 --> 03:32.620
You really know me.

03:32.710 --> 03:35.250
I've been sick of dry rations
this entire journey.

03:35.250 --> 03:38.510
I've been saving my appetite
for getting back to Jiankang.

03:43.750 --> 03:44.880
Watch your manners.

03:45.190 --> 03:46.800
Look at you,
eating like a starving ghost.

03:46.800 --> 03:48.910
How are you supposed to be
the elegant Prince Qi from the rumors?

03:48.910 --> 03:50.750
That's a bad habit
from back when we were on the run.

03:50.750 --> 03:51.840
If you eat too slowly,

03:51.840 --> 03:54.040
your food gets snatched and you starve.

03:54.280 --> 03:56.280
I still haven't managed to shake it.

03:59.240 --> 03:59.820
Yizhi,

04:00.430 --> 04:03.230
thank you for helping
with the matter in Yongzhou.

04:03.710 --> 04:04.400
Wuyi,

04:05.280 --> 04:06.410
is something wrong?

04:06.680 --> 04:08.140
I waited here for you today

04:08.590 --> 04:11.000
because I want you
to stay out of the capital for now.

04:11.000 --> 04:13.400
Something is about to happen
in the capital.

04:13.400 --> 04:14.630
Don't tell me it's Prince Changsha again.

04:14.630 --> 04:15.190
No.

04:16.269 --> 04:16.950
It's me.

04:17.630 --> 04:18.560
What did you do?

04:20.000 --> 04:21.800
I'm taking a secondary consort.

04:22.000 --> 04:22.950
Again?

04:24.040 --> 04:25.370
Isn't that a good thing?

04:25.390 --> 04:26.590
I'll be your best man.

04:26.720 --> 04:29.000
This marriage was arranged
by the Empress Dowager.

04:29.000 --> 04:30.830
The whole city is bound to be watching.

04:30.830 --> 04:32.600
And Prince Changsha has been planning
for this for a long time.

04:32.600 --> 04:34.600
There's no way he'll willingly
let me marry this lady.

04:34.600 --> 04:35.730
When the time comes,

04:35.920 --> 04:38.190
chaos is bound to break out
in the capital,

04:38.190 --> 04:40.120
and bloodshed will be inevitable.

04:40.390 --> 04:42.270
It will be safest for you to return

04:42.800 --> 04:43.560
only after everything has settled.

04:43.560 --> 04:44.560
Now I'm curious.

04:45.240 --> 04:46.870
Just which family's daughter

04:46.870 --> 04:49.040
has both you and Prince Changsha
fighting to marry her?

04:49.040 --> 04:50.830
The daughter of Grand Tutor Xie—

04:50.830 --> 04:51.630
Xie Jiayu.

04:57.950 --> 04:58.950
Prince Qi is back!

04:59.430 --> 05:01.000
It's been more than half a year.
You finally made it back.

05:01.000 --> 05:01.720
Master has really missed you.

05:01.720 --> 05:02.310
Come on, let's go drink now
that you're back.

05:02.310 --> 05:03.160
Alright, alright.

05:03.160 --> 05:03.480
Master.

05:03.480 --> 05:05.190
You should all head back first.

05:05.190 --> 05:06.120
Head back first.

05:06.240 --> 05:07.270
Master, I heard—

05:07.270 --> 05:08.130
I already know.

05:09.630 --> 05:11.120
I remember you once told me

05:11.430 --> 05:13.290
that during the unrest in Qizhou,

05:13.480 --> 05:15.560
you ran into danger
on your way back to the capital.

05:15.560 --> 05:17.790
It was Young Master Xiao
who saved you and escorted you

05:17.790 --> 05:20.360
and the Princess of Pingning County
safely back to the capital.

05:20.360 --> 05:22.600
You've known each other since then?

05:22.830 --> 05:23.270
Yes.

05:23.870 --> 05:25.800
Have you been in contact recently?

05:26.630 --> 05:28.120
It is a friendship of gentlemen.

05:28.120 --> 05:29.070
So in your eyes,

05:30.480 --> 05:32.880
Young Master Xiao is actually a gentleman?

05:33.430 --> 05:35.159
When we were young,
he once told me

05:35.159 --> 05:36.630
that, for the sake
of protecting the realm,

05:36.630 --> 05:37.190
he wanted

05:37.560 --> 05:40.090
to become the greatest general
under heaven.

05:40.430 --> 05:42.430
But after returning to the capital,

05:42.870 --> 05:45.830
he killed court officials
and intimidated the entire court.

05:45.830 --> 05:46.920
Do you still think

05:46.920 --> 05:48.980
he's the same young man
you once knew?

05:49.560 --> 05:51.120
"How shall it be said
that you have no clothes?

05:51.120 --> 05:52.360
I will share my long robes with you."

05:52.360 --> 05:53.159
It is his name,

05:53.720 --> 05:55.120
and also his aspiration.

05:56.310 --> 05:57.040
Yes.

05:57.560 --> 06:00.040
Perhaps when Xiao Sheng chose the name
"Wuyi"—"No Clothes" — for himself,

06:00.040 --> 06:01.570
he truly meant those words.

06:01.720 --> 06:02.680
But power...

06:05.190 --> 06:07.600
Power changes people.

06:08.070 --> 06:09.510
Perhaps he is no longer

06:09.510 --> 06:11.160
the person you once knew.

06:15.270 --> 06:16.430
I'll go see him myself.

06:16.430 --> 06:17.720
I'll tell him that I like Yao Yao,

06:17.720 --> 06:18.870
and ask him to call off the marriage.

06:18.870 --> 06:19.950
The Empress Dowager herself
arranged this marriage.

06:19.950 --> 06:21.040
How could it possibly be withdrawn?

06:21.040 --> 06:22.360
Then I'll go beg the Empress Dowager.

06:22.360 --> 06:24.920
Jiankang Palace is not somewhere
you can simply barge into.

06:24.920 --> 06:25.510
I know.

06:26.120 --> 06:26.680
Master,

06:27.240 --> 06:28.360
before I returned this time,

06:28.360 --> 06:30.120
I prepared a betrothal gift for Yao Yao.

06:30.120 --> 06:31.850
Please help me pass it on to her.

06:35.430 --> 06:37.030
I've already made up my mind.

06:37.040 --> 06:38.560
No matter how difficult it is,

06:38.560 --> 06:40.560
even if it means
going into Jiankang Palace,

06:40.560 --> 06:41.620
I'm willing to try.

06:42.480 --> 06:43.270
For Yao Yao,

06:44.560 --> 06:45.490
I'd do anything.

06:49.390 --> 06:51.510
[Grand Tutor's Mansion]

06:52.830 --> 06:54.310
Mao brought this for you.

06:58.120 --> 06:59.650
It's black iridescent ore.

07:00.950 --> 07:02.830
In her last letter, Yao Yao mentioned

07:02.830 --> 07:06.090
that Yongzhou produces
a rare kind of black iridescent ore

07:06.120 --> 07:08.320
that can forge the toughest black iron.

07:08.560 --> 07:09.630
Since I'm already there,

07:09.630 --> 07:11.000
I'll look for some on her behalf.

07:11.000 --> 07:14.600
It'll make an auspicious gift
when I ask for her hand in marriage.

07:15.000 --> 07:16.390
I only mentioned it once,

07:16.390 --> 07:18.720
and Mao went out of his way
to find it for me.

07:18.870 --> 07:19.480
Yao Yao,

07:20.240 --> 07:21.770
Mao has entered the palace.

07:22.480 --> 07:24.310
He wants to ask the Empress Dowager

07:24.310 --> 07:26.570
to revoke the imperial marriage decree.

07:27.070 --> 07:27.830
I knew it.

07:28.070 --> 07:29.400
Mao would never give up.

07:35.360 --> 07:38.220
You want me to revoke
the imperial marriage decree?

07:39.040 --> 07:40.630
I humbly ask
that Your Majesty grant us your blessing.

07:40.630 --> 07:42.130
Young men are naturally drawn to beauty.

07:42.130 --> 07:43.190
I understand that.

07:43.390 --> 07:43.870
But

07:45.070 --> 07:46.390
the decree has already been issued.

07:46.390 --> 07:47.990
I beg Your Majesty for mercy.

07:48.120 --> 07:50.050
In this life, I ask for nothing else

07:50.070 --> 07:51.560
but Lady Xie alone.

07:51.830 --> 07:53.230
You ask for nothing else?

07:54.510 --> 07:56.040
Your Majesty once promised

07:56.560 --> 07:59.070
that if I could find a miraculous doctor
for His Majesty,

07:59.070 --> 08:01.070
you would grant me another fiefdom.

08:01.680 --> 08:02.720
After enduring countless hardships,

08:02.720 --> 08:03.920
I finally succeeded.

08:04.140 --> 08:06.800
But now, I can forgo

08:06.890 --> 08:08.870
the land, the title, and the wealth.

08:08.870 --> 08:12.270
I ask only that Your Majesty take pity
on my sincere feelings.

08:16.800 --> 08:17.600
You can give up

08:19.680 --> 08:20.510
your land,

08:23.040 --> 08:23.920
your title,

08:24.310 --> 08:25.430
and your wealth?

08:26.920 --> 08:28.000
It seems

08:29.750 --> 08:32.549
I've played the part
of a gentle and virtuous woman

08:33.080 --> 08:35.840
for so long that some fools
have actually started to believe it.

08:35.840 --> 08:37.440
My son sits upon the throne,

08:37.870 --> 08:39.270
yet even he struggles just to survive,

08:39.270 --> 08:40.470
living like a puppet.

08:40.750 --> 08:42.200
And what are you?

08:43.390 --> 08:45.440
What is your sincerity worth?

08:45.600 --> 08:47.670
How dare you come here
and bargain with me?

08:47.670 --> 08:49.150
Everything you have now

08:49.750 --> 08:52.150
was bestowed upon you
by His Majesty and me.

08:53.120 --> 08:54.520
If I decide not to give it,

08:55.080 --> 08:56.680
then you shall have nothing.

08:57.750 --> 08:58.390
He Tian!

08:59.480 --> 09:00.360
Your servant awaits.

09:00.360 --> 09:01.720
Prince Qi trespassed
into the inner palace

09:01.720 --> 09:03.270
and spoke insolently
to the Empress Dowager.

09:03.270 --> 09:04.600
Punish him with the rod!

09:22.120 --> 09:22.630
Da.

09:25.410 --> 09:27.070
It's nothing. What happened?

09:29.270 --> 09:29.840
Lejun?

09:31.630 --> 09:32.360
Fainted?

09:35.080 --> 09:35.720
Lejun.

09:39.840 --> 09:40.440
Princess.

09:40.910 --> 09:42.270
As soon as Lejun passed out,

09:42.270 --> 09:44.550
her maids came straight to
the Grand Tutor's residence to fetch me.

09:44.550 --> 09:45.750
What happened to her?

09:46.200 --> 09:47.670
Don't tell me her old illness
has flared up again?

09:47.670 --> 09:48.530
She'll be fine.

09:49.080 --> 09:49.750
She's fine?

09:50.200 --> 09:50.840
What,

09:51.630 --> 09:53.360
Your Highness doesn't believe me?

09:53.360 --> 09:54.290
I wouldn't dare.

09:54.510 --> 09:56.120
Your Highness
is highly skilled in medicine,

09:56.120 --> 09:58.360
and it was you
who cured Lejun's chronic illness before.

09:58.360 --> 09:59.030
However,

09:59.670 --> 10:00.910
if she is truly fine,

10:00.910 --> 10:02.240
then why did she suddenly faint?

10:02.240 --> 10:04.390
She merely ate some wild fruit
by mistake.

10:04.390 --> 10:06.510
She'll recover naturally in a few days.

10:06.510 --> 10:07.360
However...

10:10.750 --> 10:12.150
something about this is strange.

10:12.150 --> 10:13.120
To fall unconscious

10:13.120 --> 10:14.450
from eating that fruit,

10:14.750 --> 10:16.790
one would have to eat
at least an entire basketful.

10:16.790 --> 10:17.910
The fruit is sour and bitter—

10:17.910 --> 10:19.030
difficult to swallow.

10:19.030 --> 10:20.830
Why would Lejun eat so much of it?

10:22.360 --> 10:24.550
Go check
whether the medicine is ready yet.

10:24.550 --> 10:25.080
Yes.

10:33.150 --> 10:35.210
I'll go check on the medicine as well.

10:41.550 --> 10:42.080
Yao Yao.

10:43.550 --> 10:44.080
Mao.

10:45.630 --> 10:47.360
My mother wouldn't let me
leave the residence,

10:47.360 --> 10:48.390
and I wanted to see you.

10:48.390 --> 10:49.720
Lejun said she had a way—

10:50.300 --> 10:52.560
I didn't expect this to be what she meant.

10:54.390 --> 10:55.320
Are you alright?

10:57.120 --> 10:58.870
Mao, you're finally back.

10:59.390 --> 11:00.120
I thought

11:00.400 --> 11:02.120
I was really going to
end up marrying someone else.

11:02.120 --> 11:03.250
The Empress Dowager

11:05.600 --> 11:07.730
still refuses to withdraw the decree.

11:08.750 --> 11:10.030
Then I won't marry him either.

11:10.030 --> 11:11.390
You're going to defy the imperial decree?

11:11.390 --> 11:11.910
Mao,

11:12.790 --> 11:14.190
I dare to defy the decree.

11:14.670 --> 11:15.330
Do you dare?

11:16.720 --> 11:17.850
Why wouldn't I dare?

11:20.870 --> 11:23.000
Father always says
I know nothing about court politics.

11:23.000 --> 11:24.000
Maybe he's right.

11:24.550 --> 11:25.240
But I do know

11:25.240 --> 11:26.720
he has no intention
of siding with Prince Jingan.

11:26.720 --> 11:28.750
And besides, the Empress Dowager
only ordered me to marry Xiao Wuyi.

11:28.750 --> 11:31.150
She never said I had to spend my life
in loving harmony with him.

11:31.150 --> 11:32.630
So as long as I complete the ceremony
on the wedding night

11:32.630 --> 11:33.960
and run away afterward,

11:34.270 --> 11:35.030
it won't count

11:35.030 --> 11:36.290
as defying the decree.

11:39.390 --> 11:41.240
I plan to go to Northern Qin,

11:41.510 --> 11:42.370
change my name,

11:42.600 --> 11:43.460
and start over.

11:44.150 --> 11:44.680
Alright.

11:45.480 --> 11:45.960
Yao Yao,

11:46.600 --> 11:48.200
no matter how powerful the Emperor
and the Empress Dowager are,

11:48.200 --> 11:50.600
there's no way they can reach
into Northern Qin to arrest anyone.

11:50.600 --> 11:51.400
It's just that

11:51.960 --> 11:53.720
the road ahead will
be fraught with danger—

11:53.720 --> 11:55.920
you must think this through carefully.

11:56.440 --> 11:57.240
To be honest,

11:57.870 --> 11:59.000
I am a little afraid.

11:59.670 --> 12:00.720
The world outside

12:00.870 --> 12:01.960
is full of killing,

12:02.150 --> 12:03.410
deceit, and betrayal.

12:03.630 --> 12:05.080
But I can't let fear condemn me

12:05.080 --> 12:05.840
to spending the rest of my life

12:05.840 --> 12:07.370
trapped in Jingan Mansion.

12:07.720 --> 12:08.270
Yao Yao,

12:08.910 --> 12:10.480
no matter how disastrous this may become,

12:10.480 --> 12:12.080
if you want to go through with it,

12:12.080 --> 12:14.140
I'll be with you every step of the way.

12:18.790 --> 12:20.030
What about Lejun?

12:20.150 --> 12:21.120
What will happen to her?

12:21.120 --> 12:22.600
Of course she's coming with us.

12:22.600 --> 12:23.330
Don't worry—

12:23.360 --> 12:24.000
she likes you

12:24.000 --> 12:25.750
far more than she likes me,
her own brother.

12:25.750 --> 12:26.360
Besides,

12:26.360 --> 12:27.790
back when we were fleeing
for our lives,

12:27.790 --> 12:31.120
we already promised
that we'd face life and death together.

12:31.840 --> 12:32.900
Wait here a moment.

12:37.200 --> 12:37.930
What's this?

12:42.670 --> 12:43.390
This...

12:43.720 --> 12:45.250
can be our token of promise.

12:55.200 --> 12:57.260
I didn't expect things would still be

12:57.390 --> 13:01.390
so lively and carefree at Wuyi's place
with the wedding so close at hand.

13:15.240 --> 13:16.480
Is this for your cousin?

13:16.480 --> 13:17.340
Don't touch it.

13:20.030 --> 13:22.150
Mao, coming by this late at night...

13:23.670 --> 13:25.630
you must have something important to say.

13:25.630 --> 13:27.630
I assume you've already guessed it.

13:28.360 --> 13:31.080
Lady Xie is the woman I love.

13:33.360 --> 13:34.240
Is that all?

13:34.390 --> 13:35.550
She loves me too.

13:36.870 --> 13:38.510
A gifted man and a beautiful woman—

13:38.510 --> 13:40.110
you are indeed well matched.

13:40.360 --> 13:42.620
I hope you will call off this engagement.

13:44.600 --> 13:45.840
And if I refuse?

13:47.320 --> 13:48.600
You pressured the Empress Dowager
into issuing the marriage decree

13:48.600 --> 13:50.910
for no reason other than
to disrupt Prince Changsha's plans.

13:50.910 --> 13:52.310
But Xie Jiayu is a person.

13:53.270 --> 13:54.360
She has feelings

13:54.360 --> 13:55.200
and a life of her own.

13:55.200 --> 13:56.400
She shouldn't have to

13:56.750 --> 13:58.790
become an innocent sacrifice
to your schemes.

13:58.790 --> 13:59.510
Mao,

14:00.840 --> 14:03.240
there are no innocent people
in this world.

14:06.320 --> 14:07.980
The other day, Master asked me

14:08.080 --> 14:09.210
whether, in my eyes,

14:10.150 --> 14:11.950
Xiao Wuyi was still a gentleman.

14:12.080 --> 14:13.080
Of course I'm not.

14:13.840 --> 14:14.840
Nor do I want to be.

14:15.360 --> 14:16.360
In an age of chaos,

14:17.550 --> 14:19.360
gentlemen either fade into obscurity

14:19.360 --> 14:21.120
or die with their ambitions
buried in the dust.

14:21.120 --> 14:22.030
I will be

14:23.960 --> 14:25.490
the one who holds the blade.

14:26.240 --> 14:27.030
Xiao Wuyi...

14:27.870 --> 14:28.960
are you still the same young man

14:28.960 --> 14:30.720
who once saved me from danger?

14:42.150 --> 14:44.150
This alliance cannot be called off.

14:44.390 --> 14:46.590
The wedding must proceed as scheduled.

14:51.150 --> 14:51.750
Fine.

14:52.390 --> 14:53.450
On the wedding day,

14:53.670 --> 14:55.670
Xie Jiayu and I will leave together.

14:55.670 --> 14:57.270
Where could you possibly go?

14:57.320 --> 14:58.360
To the ends of the earth.

14:58.360 --> 14:59.030
Anywhere.

14:59.160 --> 15:00.840
Then you shouldn't
have told me.

15:00.840 --> 15:03.840
I'm telling you
because I still consider you a friend.

15:04.230 --> 15:05.430
If you want to stop me,

15:07.000 --> 15:07.870
then just do it.

15:09.860 --> 15:11.520
You're just as naïve as she is.

15:25.800 --> 15:28.060
Mao actually managed to bring this back.

15:28.630 --> 15:29.240
With this,

15:29.380 --> 15:32.240
we won't get lost when we run away
on the wedding day.

15:37.240 --> 15:37.840
Mother...

15:46.150 --> 15:47.080
you already

15:47.850 --> 15:49.380
knew all along, didn't you?

15:54.200 --> 15:54.790
Mother,

15:55.870 --> 15:56.510
thank you.

16:00.200 --> 16:00.800
Mother...

16:02.790 --> 16:04.960
What are you bowing for out of nowhere?

16:06.240 --> 16:06.960
I know

16:07.670 --> 16:08.670
that the last time

16:09.200 --> 16:12.060
I had Lejun eat those wild berries
to get you to come,

16:12.270 --> 16:13.480
you had already noticed

16:13.480 --> 16:15.240
I was hiding among the maids.

16:15.790 --> 16:17.520
You just chose not to expose me.

16:17.630 --> 16:19.270
Later, you even went along with it

16:19.270 --> 16:21.080
and took me to Prince Qi's residence.

16:21.080 --> 16:23.910
And these past few days,
there's no way you wouldn't

16:23.910 --> 16:25.790
have noticed everything I've been
secretly preparing in the residence.

16:25.790 --> 16:27.550
You simply turned a blind eye

16:29.120 --> 16:31.180
because you intended to let me leave.

16:32.790 --> 16:33.440
Mother,

16:34.480 --> 16:35.480
I have failed you.

16:36.440 --> 16:38.900
I've always upset you ever
since I was young,

16:39.120 --> 16:42.180
and now I'm forcing you
to make such a difficult choice.

16:46.270 --> 16:47.080
You're wrong.

16:52.320 --> 16:53.550
The daughter I want

16:54.440 --> 16:57.030
is not some puppet
who only knows how to obey me,

16:57.030 --> 16:57.960
but a young woman

16:58.550 --> 17:00.210
who truly knows what she wants

17:00.870 --> 17:02.720
and what she ought to do.

17:03.910 --> 17:06.040
You've been through quite a bit by now.

17:06.069 --> 17:09.109
You should understand that the world
outside and the Grand Tutor's residence

17:09.109 --> 17:11.109
are two entirely different worlds.

17:11.240 --> 17:13.440
Now that you know
how cruel the outside world can be,

17:13.440 --> 17:14.900
you still intend to leave?

17:17.310 --> 17:18.109
I do.

17:27.440 --> 17:28.310
Then go.

17:29.350 --> 17:30.410
But remember this:

17:30.640 --> 17:33.170
make absolutely sure
you're fully prepared.

17:39.110 --> 17:40.730
Mother, don't worry.

17:41.270 --> 17:43.130
Lejun and Mao will both be with me.

17:43.480 --> 17:44.400
Mao said

17:44.590 --> 17:46.320
he'll take care of everything.

17:46.510 --> 17:47.070
No.

17:48.590 --> 17:49.480
What I mean is

17:50.270 --> 17:52.870
that you yourself
must also be fully prepared.

17:54.550 --> 17:55.410
Remember this:

17:56.200 --> 17:57.110
no matter when,

17:58.110 --> 17:59.640
the one you can truly rely on

18:00.310 --> 18:01.570
is never your parents,

18:01.620 --> 18:02.420
your husband,

18:02.450 --> 18:03.450
or your children.

18:04.920 --> 18:06.000
It is yourself.

18:19.070 --> 18:20.800
Over here, over here! Hurry up.

18:21.780 --> 18:22.820
Make sure you wipe it properly.

18:22.820 --> 18:23.480
Alright!

18:29.590 --> 18:31.440
Xiao Wuyi did indeed
risk returning to the capital.

18:31.440 --> 18:33.270
There are at most 100 household guards
inside Jingan Mansion,

18:33.270 --> 18:34.880
and everything outside the city
remains normal as well.

18:34.880 --> 18:36.720
The Beifu Army
is still stationed at the border.

18:36.720 --> 18:39.720
As for the border garrison—
he wouldn't dare make any rash move.

18:39.720 --> 18:40.780
A bride-stealing?

18:41.440 --> 18:42.480
It's nothing more than an attempt

18:42.480 --> 18:44.590
to stop me from securing the support
of the noble clans.

18:44.590 --> 18:46.870
The Beifu Army suffered heavy losses
at Jiuzhang Plain.

18:46.870 --> 18:50.330
We must not wait for the border forces
to regroup before we act.

18:59.370 --> 19:01.420
[Prince Qi's Mansion]

19:35.110 --> 19:35.830
Father.

19:36.880 --> 19:37.480
Mother.

19:42.450 --> 19:45.870
♪ A dying memory glimmers low ♪

19:44.750 --> 19:45.310
Father.

19:46.170 --> 19:49.850
♪ You appear, but I can't hold you so ♪

19:46.240 --> 19:47.680
I prepared a gift for you.

19:49.960 --> 19:54.320
♪ Time itself comes to a sudden halt ♪

19:54.680 --> 19:57.380
♪ So desolate ♪

19:55.920 --> 19:57.890
It's for massaging your shoulders.

19:57.890 --> 19:58.400
Look,

19:57.960 --> 20:01.620
♪ I traded obsession for this loss ♪

19:59.310 --> 20:00.170
Just like this.

20:01.650 --> 20:05.190
♪ If I could lay my heart bare and cross ♪

20:05.380 --> 20:10.710
♪ Would you once more have pity on me ♪

20:11.350 --> 20:14.790
♪ If the heavens should change
and fate tear me apart ♪

20:13.080 --> 20:14.030
I understand

20:14.820 --> 20:18.810
♪ Yet still cannot undo one beat
of my heart's art ♪

20:15.750 --> 20:18.550
this is your way
of showing filial devotion.

20:18.950 --> 20:22.660
♪ I've traveled so far—
the day I find you again ♪

20:22.680 --> 20:25.980
♪ I fear you might have forgotten me ♪

20:23.920 --> 20:25.160
My dear Yao Yao...

20:28.590 --> 20:30.190
you look so beautiful today.

20:37.400 --> 20:37.960
Father,

20:39.920 --> 20:42.250
if I am no longer by your side
in the future,

20:42.960 --> 20:44.960
you must take good care of yourself.

20:45.790 --> 20:47.200
Silly child,

20:51.000 --> 20:52.070
why are you crying?

20:53.350 --> 20:54.610
I am not crying either.

20:55.110 --> 20:56.750
We'll see each other again someday,

20:56.750 --> 20:57.350
won't we?

21:02.550 --> 21:04.000
It's my fault

21:05.960 --> 21:08.490
for letting you be burdened
by the Xie family.

21:09.130 --> 21:10.860
If you hadn't been my daughter,

21:13.160 --> 21:14.270
your life

21:16.070 --> 21:17.530
would have been far freer.

21:20.240 --> 21:21.970
Please don't say that, Father.

21:23.480 --> 21:24.880
Being born your daughter

21:26.750 --> 21:28.010
has made me very happy.

21:39.920 --> 21:40.590
Mother.

21:46.880 --> 21:49.310
The auspicious hour has arrived.

22:05.960 --> 22:07.020
Young Master Xiao,

22:07.440 --> 22:08.640
it's been a long time.

22:11.110 --> 22:12.440
When have I ever met you?

22:13.510 --> 22:14.000
Fine.

22:14.590 --> 22:16.480
It doesn't matter
if you don't remember me.

22:16.480 --> 22:17.640
After tonight,

22:18.070 --> 22:20.200
I'll make sure you remember me deeply,

22:20.310 --> 22:21.710
for the rest of your life.

22:21.750 --> 22:22.880
I look forward to it.

22:24.110 --> 22:25.170
Alright, alright.

22:25.550 --> 22:28.240
Don't say things like that in public.

22:29.440 --> 22:30.440
Off you go now—

22:31.240 --> 22:33.040
don't miss the auspicious hour.

22:59.480 --> 23:00.160
Xiao Wuyi,

23:00.480 --> 23:03.140
a daughter of the Xie family
is not so easily won.

23:03.310 --> 23:04.720
You—get down here.

23:19.850 --> 23:20.910
It's not straight.

23:37.350 --> 23:38.830
Xiao Wuyi, let go of me!

23:39.140 --> 23:39.900
Xiao Wuyi,

23:40.110 --> 23:41.270
let go of me!

23:47.680 --> 23:49.270
Xiao Wuyi, let go of me!

23:49.400 --> 23:50.110
Xiao Wuyi,

23:53.350 --> 23:54.440
let go!

23:57.110 --> 23:58.310
Lord Li, Madam Li.

23:58.480 --> 24:00.740
-Congratulations.
-Congratulations.

24:03.430 --> 24:04.080
Mr. Zhang, please come in.

24:04.080 --> 24:05.490
Xiao Wuyi, let go of me!

24:05.920 --> 24:07.030
You jerk! You villain!

24:07.030 --> 24:07.880
Put me down!

24:09.830 --> 24:11.680
Xiao Wuyi, let go of me!

24:11.980 --> 24:13.980
Let go of me! Put me down!

24:14.640 --> 24:15.270
Xiao Wuyi,

24:16.550 --> 24:17.510
put me down!

24:19.640 --> 24:21.640
Xiao Wuyi, put me down.

24:23.160 --> 24:24.160
Xiao Wuyi, you...

24:24.350 --> 24:24.880
Yan Yue.

24:25.000 --> 24:26.200
-Yes.
-Take her to the bridal chamber.

24:26.200 --> 24:27.400
Don't give her any food

24:27.400 --> 24:28.350
or water.

24:29.200 --> 24:30.600
Xiao Wuyi, just you wait.

24:30.610 --> 24:33.030
Tonight, I'll make you regret this
for the rest of your life.

24:33.030 --> 24:34.920
Is this meant to be a show of force
against the Xie family?

24:34.920 --> 24:35.920
More than that.

24:36.000 --> 24:38.930
The one being humiliated
is Grand Tutor Xie himself.

24:41.200 --> 24:43.350
Take good care
of my secondary consort.

24:43.350 --> 24:45.920
I don't want to hear a single sound
from her tonight.

24:45.920 --> 24:46.480
Yes.

24:47.230 --> 24:50.690
Your Highness, the wedding rites
haven't been completed yet.

24:51.440 --> 24:52.700
Since you're all here,

24:52.960 --> 24:55.720
drink with me tonight until we're
completely drunk and no one leaves sober.

24:55.720 --> 24:57.050
None of you are leaving.

24:57.270 --> 24:57.750
Wuyi,

24:58.110 --> 24:59.590
tonight is the wedding
bestowed by the Empress Dowager.

24:59.590 --> 25:00.550
-Let's go.
-Don't—

25:00.550 --> 25:01.750
Come on, let's drink!

25:07.590 --> 25:08.270
Your Highness,

25:08.270 --> 25:09.960
most of the court officials invited to
the wedding banquet have already arrived.

25:09.960 --> 25:12.960
The remaining senior ministers
are also on their way.

25:13.160 --> 25:14.690
Proceed according to plan.

25:15.550 --> 25:19.080
My life and death, my honor and disgrace—
all depend on tonight.

25:19.350 --> 25:19.920
Yes.

25:23.000 --> 25:23.550
My Lady,

25:23.550 --> 25:25.010
Xiao Wuyi is going too far.

25:25.440 --> 25:27.680
He actually had you carried
all the way back to the mansion—

25:27.680 --> 25:28.680
and on top of that…

25:28.720 --> 25:30.000
on your wedding night,

25:30.000 --> 25:32.430
he's drinking and making merry
with dancing girls.

25:32.430 --> 25:33.490
It doesn't matter.

25:33.640 --> 25:37.300
In any case, the one who will be
utterly humiliated tonight is him.

25:44.270 --> 25:44.920
One at the door,

25:44.920 --> 25:46.450
and two outside the window.

25:47.480 --> 25:49.830
Even the numbers line up exactly
with the map.

25:49.830 --> 25:51.110
Heaven is helping me!

25:52.270 --> 25:53.270
Are you all ready?

25:54.200 --> 25:55.930
A top-grade sleeping draught.

26:00.160 --> 26:01.160
Is anyone outside?

26:01.160 --> 26:02.360
My Lady is in trouble—

26:02.400 --> 26:03.310
someone help!

26:04.240 --> 26:05.570
Hurry! Come in, come in!

26:08.770 --> 26:09.450
Let's go.

26:23.510 --> 26:25.160
How come there isn't a single soul

26:25.160 --> 26:26.890
in this entire Jingan Mansion?

26:28.590 --> 26:29.450
Ugh… it stinks.

26:34.110 --> 26:34.750
No, no—

26:34.880 --> 26:35.870
this is the outhouse.

26:35.870 --> 26:37.200
The main gate is to the east...

26:37.200 --> 26:38.160
The kitchen's over there.

26:38.160 --> 26:38.890
Hurry, move!

26:44.110 --> 26:45.070
Don't block the entrance—

26:45.070 --> 26:46.200
we're serving food!

26:46.640 --> 26:48.550
Douzi, take the slop out!

26:48.920 --> 26:49.450
Alright!

26:51.790 --> 26:52.320
Let's go.

26:56.550 --> 26:58.080
What are you all doing here?

27:00.440 --> 27:00.970
Let's go.

27:07.960 --> 27:08.560
How was it?

27:08.880 --> 27:10.210
Did we seem real enough?

27:11.510 --> 27:12.770
He was pretending too?

27:12.890 --> 27:16.220
He wasn't.  You still need someone real
in the mix, don't you?

27:26.590 --> 27:28.720
Your Highness, they've already left.

27:30.160 --> 27:30.890
Which route?

27:31.590 --> 27:33.830
As expected,
the bride chose the back kitchen path.

27:33.830 --> 27:36.490
She just took several wrong turns
along the way.

27:36.750 --> 27:38.550
This is the hairpin she dropped.

27:41.920 --> 27:44.050
Even with a map, she can't find her way.

27:44.240 --> 27:45.170
She is so stupid.

27:47.350 --> 27:48.160
It's bad—

27:48.310 --> 27:49.570
the bride has escaped!

27:53.350 --> 27:54.280
What did you say?

28:12.790 --> 28:14.920
In my mansion,
from the guards to the gardeners,

28:14.920 --> 28:16.750
groundskeepers, and stablehands—

28:16.750 --> 28:18.810
every one of them knows martial arts.

28:19.000 --> 28:20.310
The moment she steps out
of the courtyard gate,

28:20.310 --> 28:21.510
she will be detected.

28:21.550 --> 28:22.750
If you plan to escape,

28:24.300 --> 28:25.560
you would need my help.

28:28.400 --> 28:30.200
This is the map of Jingan Mansion.

28:30.200 --> 28:31.960
Xie Jiayu will need it
if she tries to escape the wedding.

28:31.960 --> 28:34.420
But this wedding
must proceed as scheduled.

28:34.660 --> 28:37.110
because this is the day
I have chosen for Prince Changsha

28:37.110 --> 28:38.510
to force the abdication.

28:38.750 --> 28:40.750
All guards of Jingan Mansion,
heed my order.

28:40.750 --> 28:41.200
-Yes!
-Yes!

28:41.200 --> 28:43.000
Search the entire city for Xie Jiayu!

28:43.000 --> 28:44.130
Yes, Your Highness.

28:45.480 --> 28:47.280
-Split up and search.
-Make way.

28:47.590 --> 28:48.270
-Move!
-Make way!

28:48.270 --> 28:49.200
What's going on?

28:49.350 --> 28:50.480
Lady Xie has fled the wedding.

28:50.480 --> 28:53.740
Xiao Wuyi has ordered his guards
to search the entire city.

28:54.620 --> 28:55.770
This Lady Xie

28:56.070 --> 28:57.670
is always full of surprises.

28:58.240 --> 29:00.650
Your Highness, Jingan Mansion
is now lightly guarded.

29:00.650 --> 29:02.380
Should we strike immediately?

29:04.110 --> 29:05.710
A heaven-sent opportunity.

29:06.750 --> 29:08.520
Issue the order
inside and outside the capital—

29:08.520 --> 29:10.000
begin the uprising at once.

29:10.000 --> 29:10.400
Yes.

29:12.120 --> 29:12.720
Attack!

29:17.160 --> 29:18.320
Take Mother and leave, quickly!

29:18.320 --> 29:19.830
Yao, be careful!

29:19.830 --> 29:20.490
Who are you?

29:20.590 --> 29:23.320
How dare you
act so recklessly in Jingan Mansion!

29:32.640 --> 29:33.240
Yuanji!

29:45.640 --> 29:46.310
Today,

29:47.400 --> 29:49.350
I shall cleanse
His Majesty's side of traitors

29:49.350 --> 29:50.550
and seize the rebels.

29:50.880 --> 29:52.790
Among all the ministers
in this courtyard,

29:52.790 --> 29:54.160
which one is a rebel?

29:54.350 --> 29:55.030
Xiao Wuyi.

29:56.110 --> 29:58.640
He brought troops back to the capital
without imperial decree,

29:58.640 --> 30:00.160
slaughtered court officials,

30:00.160 --> 30:01.030
and harbors treasonous ambitions.

30:01.030 --> 30:02.490
His crimes deserve death.

30:03.270 --> 30:03.920
Tonight,

30:05.070 --> 30:07.470
who among you
dare stand as his accomplice?

30:11.310 --> 30:12.070
It seems

30:12.680 --> 30:15.310
the only rebel here is Xiao Wuyi himself.

30:19.310 --> 30:20.880
Your Highness, we've just received word—

30:20.880 --> 30:22.940
the palace gates have been breached.

30:23.720 --> 30:25.030
Surround Jingan Mansion.

30:25.030 --> 30:26.060
With Xiao Wuyi's family

30:26.060 --> 30:27.240
and these court officials

30:27.240 --> 30:27.960
here,

30:28.240 --> 30:29.700
he won't be able to escape.

30:30.000 --> 30:31.590
The rest of you follow me
into the palace

30:31.590 --> 30:33.190
to meet the Empress Dowager.

30:33.550 --> 30:34.030
Yes.

30:39.270 --> 30:40.000
Hurry! Move!

30:46.000 --> 30:47.130
Search thoroughly—

30:47.270 --> 30:48.730
leave no alley unchecked.

30:48.790 --> 30:49.800
Yes.

30:50.440 --> 30:50.900
Search!

30:57.270 --> 30:58.130
Your Highness,

31:00.550 --> 31:03.210
Xie Jiayu's trail has been found
at Wuling Gate.

31:04.400 --> 31:05.530
Guard the city gate.

31:06.270 --> 31:07.160
I want her dead,

31:07.830 --> 31:08.790
not alive.

31:09.320 --> 31:10.320
Yes.

31:31.400 --> 31:32.680
Oh, Xiao Wuyi...

31:32.960 --> 31:34.240
You're certainly ruthless—

31:34.240 --> 31:36.440
but your eyesight isn't all that great.

31:37.480 --> 31:39.790
My Lady, it's just
that you're blessed by the True Deity.

31:39.790 --> 31:41.520
Even the heavens can't stand by

31:42.070 --> 31:43.600
and have chosen to help you.

31:45.380 --> 31:46.380
Let's go quickly,

31:46.480 --> 31:48.000
or Mao will be getting anxious.

31:48.000 --> 31:48.530
Let's go.

31:58.480 --> 31:59.160
Master?

31:59.640 --> 32:01.100
His Majesty is gravely ill

32:01.830 --> 32:05.890
and has summoned Prince Qi to enter
the palace at once and attend upon him.

32:06.920 --> 32:08.250
I can't go to the palace.

32:08.400 --> 32:09.600
I need to find Yao Yao.

32:10.880 --> 32:13.080
Guards, escort Prince Qi to the palace.

32:17.270 --> 32:17.720
Lejun!

32:17.720 --> 32:18.250
Brother!

32:23.680 --> 32:24.480
Your Highness.

32:24.480 --> 32:25.720
Are all our men assembled?

32:25.720 --> 32:26.720
Tonight, we suddenly lost all contact

32:26.720 --> 32:27.790
with forces outside the capital.

32:27.790 --> 32:31.250
Several units have been sent out,
but none have reported back.

32:32.720 --> 32:34.270
Lost contact?

32:39.030 --> 32:40.310
We won't wait any longer!

32:40.310 --> 32:42.240
Victory or defeat, honor or disgrace—
it all comes down to tonight.

32:42.240 --> 32:44.720
Enter the palace now.
Kill the Emperor and Empress Dowager!

32:44.720 --> 32:45.350
Yes!

32:46.110 --> 32:53.960
-Kill!
-Kill!

33:06.960 --> 33:07.820
Your Highness,

33:07.880 --> 33:09.440
His Majesty is not in the main hall.

33:09.440 --> 33:10.160
Not there?

33:11.310 --> 33:12.880
That sickly man can't even get out of bed—

33:12.880 --> 33:14.200
where could he possibly go?

33:14.200 --> 33:14.730
Find him!

33:15.400 --> 33:15.790
Yes.

33:20.050 --> 33:23.030
[Xuanzheng Hall]

33:24.550 --> 33:25.160
Tell me—

33:25.680 --> 33:27.160
where have you hidden
that sickly emperor?

33:27.160 --> 33:28.960
My son is the true Son of Heaven.

33:29.550 --> 33:31.410
He is protected by the True Deity.

33:31.830 --> 33:33.240
You think you can find him so easily?

33:33.240 --> 33:34.640
Don't think I'm unaware.

33:35.480 --> 33:37.240
Had you not forged the imperial edict

33:37.240 --> 33:38.550
and poisoned the late emperor,

33:38.550 --> 33:40.880
your son would never have become emperor.

33:40.920 --> 33:42.240
But Heaven sees all.

33:42.680 --> 33:43.680
Ever since he ascended the throne,

33:43.680 --> 33:45.200
he's been bedridden with illness.

33:45.200 --> 33:46.440
This is his retribution.

33:46.440 --> 33:47.240
How insolent!

33:48.240 --> 33:49.310
Utter nonsense!

33:50.400 --> 33:52.130
My son is the true Son of Heaven!

33:54.680 --> 33:55.880
Then let's see tonight

33:55.880 --> 33:57.810
who truly holds Heaven's Mandate.

33:57.980 --> 33:58.680
Guards—

34:19.550 --> 34:21.760
Why didn't you attend my wedding tonight?

34:21.760 --> 34:23.760
Xiao Wuyi, didn't you go find Xie...

34:25.480 --> 34:26.540
It doesn't matter.

34:27.670 --> 34:30.510
Tonight, my 20,000 troops have
already taken control of the capital.

34:30.510 --> 34:32.920
Those who follow me will prosper;
those who oppose me will perish.

34:32.920 --> 34:33.780
Kill Xiao Wuyi!

34:38.320 --> 34:39.480
What are you afraid of?

34:39.480 --> 34:43.679
Whoever kills Xiao Wuyi shall be granted
a fief of ten thousand households!

34:51.710 --> 34:54.030
You mean those forces
outside the capital?

34:54.030 --> 34:55.630
I've already wiped them out.

34:57.000 --> 34:57.930
What do you mean?

35:00.550 --> 35:01.030
Kneel!

35:01.340 --> 35:02.150
-Spare us, Your Highness!
-Please spare us!

35:02.150 --> 35:03.010
Where are they?

35:03.190 --> 35:04.390
Where are the others?

35:16.150 --> 35:19.010
-Please spare us, Your Highness!
-Please spare us!

35:19.880 --> 35:20.810
No… I won't lose.

35:21.590 --> 35:22.840
I absolutely will not lose.

35:22.840 --> 35:24.440
I still have Jingan Mansion,

35:24.710 --> 35:25.910
all those ministers,

35:26.030 --> 35:28.030
and your entire family.  If you dare—

35:30.440 --> 35:31.760
His Highness has given the order—

35:31.760 --> 35:32.400
kill!

35:32.840 --> 35:33.360
Yes.

35:33.710 --> 35:34.960
Who dares take another step forward?

35:34.960 --> 35:36.590
I am the Princess of Jingan Mansion,

35:36.590 --> 35:38.280
the Empress Dowager's own niece.

35:38.280 --> 35:40.540
Let's see who dares
lay a hand on me today!

35:45.110 --> 35:46.030
Did you think I didn't know

35:46.030 --> 35:48.230
you would move against Jingan Mansion?

35:48.280 --> 35:51.230
How dare a useless drunkard from
pleasure-filled Jiankang City like you

35:51.230 --> 35:52.960
play war games with me?

36:01.020 --> 36:02.090
[Xiao Ju, Prince Jing'an]

36:02.480 --> 36:03.000
Father.

36:03.960 --> 36:04.700
Are you alright?

36:04.700 --> 36:05.230
I'm fine.

36:05.280 --> 36:06.110
Your Highness.

36:06.110 --> 36:06.670
My Lady.

36:07.740 --> 36:11.140
Lady Rui, have you not been in the mansion
these past few days?

36:11.510 --> 36:13.280
Due to urgent military matters,

36:13.280 --> 36:15.880
Wuyi asked her to guide me
outside the capital.

36:16.880 --> 36:17.440
Yao.

36:17.960 --> 36:18.760
It's alright.

36:19.110 --> 36:20.440
All of you, listen well!

36:21.230 --> 36:23.760
Prince Changsha
has attempted a palace coup.

36:24.150 --> 36:27.360
The Beifu Army has marched thousands
of miles to suppress the rebellion.

36:27.360 --> 36:28.630
At this very moment,

36:28.880 --> 36:32.710
my son Xiao Wuyi has already captured
Prince Changsha alive within the palace.

36:32.710 --> 36:35.400
Surrender immediately!

36:37.960 --> 36:40.840
or you will all be slain without mercy.

36:42.840 --> 36:44.100
The Beifu Army is back…

36:44.360 --> 36:47.490
Is this truly suppressing a rebellion…
or starting one?

37:00.550 --> 37:01.680
I can't accept this!

37:02.990 --> 37:04.670
I'm unwilling to keep being trampled

37:04.670 --> 37:06.840
under the feet of that useless emperor.

37:06.840 --> 37:07.770
Do you regret it?

37:10.280 --> 37:11.030
Regret?

37:13.320 --> 37:15.760
I have never felt so alive and satisfied.

37:17.110 --> 37:19.280
Xiao Wuyi, do you think killing me

37:19.590 --> 37:21.990
will avenge the Beifu Army
who died in vain?

37:22.400 --> 37:24.550
Don't think you're any different from me—

37:24.550 --> 37:26.360
don't you also want
to kill that useless emperor

37:26.360 --> 37:28.620
and take his place in this Xianyang Hall?

37:34.590 --> 37:35.360
Aunt…

37:35.920 --> 37:36.720
Your Majesty…

37:37.510 --> 37:39.670
Xiao Wuyi will kill you both
sooner or later.

37:39.670 --> 37:40.960
Perhaps even tonight.

37:45.440 --> 37:47.230
How foolish and self-deceived.

37:47.230 --> 37:49.160
You don't even know who is the piece

37:49.230 --> 37:51.160
and who is the player on this board.

37:53.030 --> 37:54.920
I originally believed Prince Changsha

37:54.920 --> 37:56.110
had secretly colluded
with Wonderful Master,

37:56.110 --> 37:58.070
bribing the Armory Director
in my army

37:58.070 --> 38:00.400
to purchase a batch
of defective repeating crossbows.

38:00.400 --> 38:01.760
But it turned out Wonderful Master

38:01.760 --> 38:02.960
didn't even know you.

38:04.110 --> 38:06.370
The real mastermind behind the purchase

38:07.400 --> 38:08.730
is the Empress Dowager.

38:11.630 --> 38:15.000
The one who most wants to see me
and Prince Changsha destroy each other…

38:15.000 --> 38:16.600
is also the Empress Dowager.

38:28.070 --> 38:30.320
Young Master Xiao,
you are indeed perceptive.

38:30.320 --> 38:31.800
The official in charge
of military supplies, Treasurer Wei,

38:31.800 --> 38:33.460
is an ally of Prince Changsha.

38:33.920 --> 38:36.250
As long as you handed him
the design plans,

38:36.440 --> 38:39.360
he would complete the rest
of the scheme with Prince Changsha,

38:39.360 --> 38:42.590
and eliminate both me and the Beifu Army.

38:43.670 --> 38:44.730
Just like tonight—

38:45.510 --> 38:48.150
Your Majesty neither mobilized troops
nor prepared defenses,

38:48.150 --> 38:50.920
betting that even though
I knew this palace entry was a trap,

38:50.920 --> 38:53.850
I would still refuse
to let Prince Changsha succeed.

38:55.000 --> 38:55.660
So tonight,

38:56.760 --> 38:58.030
Your Majesty's target

38:58.030 --> 38:59.630
is not only Prince Changsha…

39:00.320 --> 39:01.440
but me as well.

39:10.590 --> 39:12.720
What a perfect invitation into a trap.

39:14.360 --> 39:15.110
I always thought

39:15.110 --> 39:17.710
you were nothing
more than a useless old woman.

39:17.880 --> 39:19.080
I didn't expect this.

39:21.190 --> 39:21.840
Fine—

39:23.400 --> 39:24.330
I lose this round

39:25.550 --> 39:26.680
without complaint.

39:36.850 --> 39:38.880
Since you already knew
tonight was a trap,

39:38.880 --> 39:40.190
why did you still come?

39:42.400 --> 39:43.510
Because I did not want

39:43.510 --> 39:45.710
Jiankang to run red with blood tonight.

39:47.150 --> 39:47.630
But

39:49.030 --> 39:51.150
I must demand justice
for the 30,000 fallen soldiers

39:51.150 --> 39:52.150
of the Beifu Army.

39:56.590 --> 39:57.630
Brave indeed.

39:58.110 --> 39:59.550
I can spare your life.

39:59.880 --> 40:02.150
If you are willing
to surrender your military command,

40:02.150 --> 40:03.610
I will grant you immunity.

40:03.630 --> 40:04.960
And if I refuse?

40:08.030 --> 40:08.840
Empress Dowager,

40:08.840 --> 40:10.590
I submitted the roster
of our fallen soldiers

40:10.590 --> 40:11.520
half a month ago.

40:11.710 --> 40:13.400
I wonder if you have read it?

40:14.280 --> 40:14.960
Not yet.

40:15.840 --> 40:16.670
Shi Yuchun,

40:17.710 --> 40:18.550
46 years old—

40:18.920 --> 40:21.190
stabbed over 100 times,
yet died without kneeling.

40:21.190 --> 40:22.960
Xie Han, a veteran of the Beifu Army.

40:22.960 --> 40:24.320
He spent his entire life at war,

40:24.320 --> 40:26.110
and could have laid down his armor
and returned home—

40:26.110 --> 40:29.030
but his homeland had
already fallen to Northern Qin.

40:29.030 --> 40:30.360
He said he has nowhere else to go

40:30.360 --> 40:32.630
and wishes to spend the rest
of his life in the army.

40:32.630 --> 40:33.360
This time,

40:34.840 --> 40:35.960
he truly did die—

40:36.190 --> 40:38.940
his body trampled
into a pulp beneath enemy hooves.

40:38.940 --> 40:41.050
Zhang Ji, my most trusted deputy.

40:41.440 --> 40:44.500
He personally set fire
to the vine-armored grain depot

40:44.840 --> 40:46.970
and perished together
with the enemy.

40:47.150 --> 40:49.080
Does Your Majesty know any of this?

40:49.320 --> 40:51.880
Do you, sitting here
in Jiankang, even care?

40:56.960 --> 40:59.360
That is why I will not
surrender my command—

40:59.400 --> 41:00.660
because apart from me,

41:02.020 --> 41:03.590
no one else cares about their lives.

41:03.590 --> 41:04.510
Xiao Wuyi,

41:06.030 --> 41:08.110
the Beifu Army entered the capital
without an imperial decree.

41:08.110 --> 41:09.550
Are you trying to rebel?

41:16.510 --> 41:19.440
But you will end up returning to Jiankang
without the Emperor's decree.

41:19.440 --> 41:21.170
What about mobilizing troops?

41:22.280 --> 41:24.210
Prince Changsha seeks rebellion—

41:24.590 --> 41:25.450
what about you?

41:27.630 --> 41:28.430
Your Majesty,

41:30.270 --> 41:32.270
all I want is peace across the realm.

41:33.480 --> 41:35.610
Is Your Majesty willing to grant that?

41:41.230 --> 41:43.030
Have you ever heard the war drums

41:43.230 --> 41:44.630
of the Beifu Army?

41:46.840 --> 41:48.770
One hundred thousand Beifu troops

41:49.360 --> 41:50.550
are just outside the city now.
